    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300920/extras/265a8bb44eb625bdc087a44d874c332b.avif?t=1749385644\" width=616 height=72 /></span>你被几个街头混混胁迫参加了一场入室抢劫。他们在把你带到受害者的家门口时告诉你说，这间屋子里面只住着三个女人，所以这票根本就没有失败的可能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你蹑手蹑脚地走进了屋子，开始按照同伙的吩咐搜索起了值钱的东西。房间里黑得伸手不见五指，尽管你没发现什么值得拿走的物品，但是一切到目前为止都很顺利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直到突如其来的尖叫声吓得你手足无措……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300920/extras/7ae6132ac45a2ce7dc503f85e16503d7.avif?t=1749385644\" width=616 height=72 /></span>您的任务是利用手边的一切资源与道具，逃出未知的恐怖存在的手掌心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您所做出的每一个选择都会影响剧情的发展。在这场游戏中没有生存与死亡以外的规则——尽一切努力存活到最后吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300920/extras/0a7c61414714446a0e0ba5c275e83dd7.avif?t=1749385644\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300920/extras/4904265e4b5a736f193683101943287f.avif?t=1749385644\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300920/extras/ec5aa36e85e914a891173390b039ea98.avif?t=1749385644\" width=616 height=399 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300920/extras/2299ee19d259d16adc626bfb01be0428.avif?t=1749385644\" width=616 height=72 /></span><strong>逃脱类恐怖游戏</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潜行与躲藏将会成为这部游戏的主旋律，屏幕前的您的任务就是尽可能地生存下去，找到逃出生天的机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精心绘制的贴图</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本部作品的贴图由多名知名画师精心绘制，只为给您带来最难忘的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多种结局可供收集</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通向出口的路不止一条，而逃走的方法也不止一种。您究竟能否将这些结局全部收入囊中呢？</p>",
